{"tid":1078664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"謝 婷 婷 男 友 鷹 眼 傳 戀 上 Lady Gaga","createTime":"2019-03-26T12:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T06:24:10.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"008c3f936540bb3c5d721645520a73b786ed418f","tid":1078664,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:05:50.000Z","msg":"美國流行天后Lady Gaga早前憑《星夢情深》（A Star Is Born）風光贏回首座奧斯卡後，隨即確認跟未婚夫分手，不過近日有傳她極速走出情傷，戀上「鷹眼」謝洛美維拿（Jeremy Renner）。據外媒報道，有知情人士透露目擊二人密密約會，謝洛美更帶6歲囡囡見Gaga，關係呼之欲出。<br />\n32歲的Lady Gaga上月第二次在訂婚後宣佈取消婚約，跟拍拖兩年、訂婚五個月的經理人未婚夫Christian Carino分道揚鑣，之後傳出烏龍孕訊，Gaga即時於社交網站澄清目前正在「孕育」第六張大碟。<br />\n談到謝洛美的感情生活，本地的謝婷婷曾多次默認與謝洛美拍拖；17年7月，謝洛美維納在美國接受《蘋果》專訪時，已開腔否認跟謝婷婷是情侶關係。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190322/large/1553224841_c837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190322%2Flarge%2F1553224841_c837.jpg&h=abd43eff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12b3de34ffe26e1aff4de2b5579fb39d2a56ec60","tid":1078664,"uid":132587,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"謝婷婷真係好撚柒<br />\n單戀都拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc4c25e7ac99c8e02ef1a194fbdc104714b3110","tid":1078664,"uid":96728,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"12b3de34ffe26e1aff4de2b5579fb39d2a56ec60","tid":1078664,"uid":132587,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"謝婷婷真係好撚柒<br />\n單戀都拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"似ons <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbefa1604b54c7df71b5b2a51789090754a726e","tid":1078664,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"